# AI Memory Palace

When a task involves long-term memory, project notes, continuation state, migration, audit, or an Agent-readable index:

1. Read `SKILL.md`.
2. Read `ai-memory-index.md`.
3. Use `ai-memory-template.md` for new project memory.

Organize memory into: 入口, 门厅, 地图, 展厅, 工坊, 档案室, 警示墙, 工作台, 出口.

This directory is the source of truth. Downstream projects should reference it with a small local rule instead of copying the full method.
